{"tid":2285000,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯拖時間被球證訓斥：請尊重一點！","createTime":"2020-11-13T18:10:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T06:20:02.000Z","uid":173952,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a1fced40d511382c8ae85bb38bf9b25b04b84e29","tid":2285000,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T18:10:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QrFK6yg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQrFK6yg.jpg&h=fce6f514&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歐洲足協TV以球證為主題的電視片《Man in the Middle》將在11月16日開播，在預告片中，人們看到了一個有趣的幕後細節。<br />\n<br />\n  2019年4月在歐聯4強首回合中，巴塞隆拿主場3比0擊敗利物浦，比賽最後階段，美斯（Lionel Messi）試圖拖時間，而荷蘭球證庫伊佩斯似乎有些不耐煩，他衝著美斯喊道：「美斯，得了吧，展現點尊重！」然後他指著印有「尊重」字樣的臂章，繼續說：「每次你都這麼做，得了吧！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  在4強第二回合的比賽中，利物浦回到主場以4比0擊敗巴塞，完成了大逆轉。"},{"pid":"805b6626d2f558dc43280d4567fec1a1807a8294","tid":2285000,"uid":8500,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T18:28:28.000Z","msg":"請尊重 謝謝"},{"pid":"3585fdd9e5a5132dd9f7c8e39c6428566ab55efa","tid":2285000,"uid":101307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T20:48:23.000Z","msg":"減到咁瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請尊重，謝謝！"},{"pid":"4eca60fdbd3238340597e96492daaa4514c335cb","tid":2285000,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T01:35:28.000Z","msg":"原來係呢場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1563365f2b9959ea0677c4595ade012a74d534d9","tid":2285000,"uid":287385,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T03:07:22.000Z","msg":"我朗無論贏緊定輸緊，去到最後幾分鐘都會爭取每一個機會入波，呢樣阿西真係完全比唔上"},{"pid":"705bbe108895de505ab04a761e